04:28.800 --> 04:34.160
In all seriousness, it could wipe out humanity. At least that's according to Google DeepMind's

04:34.160 --> 04:38.160
senior scientist Marcus Hutter and Oxford researchers Michael Cohen and Michael Osborne.

04:38.800 --> 04:41.760
